reviewText: American Degenerate is another solid effort by Jim Norton, he performed a great set and I love the fact that it was filmed in Boston. I definitely recommend American Degenerate to anyone who is a Jim Norton fan. Monster Rain is another hilarious must see special by Jim Norton as well.
This guy is funny and politically correct in our opinions
My uncle Paul bought this for me. If I had only known the horrible things I would have to endure as a result, I would do it all again. It's so funny that my anus bled.

i first saw a Jim Norton show on epic and fell in love with Jim Norton as a comedian. anyone who wants to laugh and laugh i truly recommend Jim's show to anyone. he is just an out of sight comedian who anyone should fall in love with his show or shows.
